                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="72782" author="benbennett" created="Thu, 17 Nov 2011 09:54:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A quick work around was to add a timeout for the connection close method call inside spring-amqp . I don&apos;t know what a good default would be and adding property to the AbstractConnection class might be the way to go. &lt;br/&gt;
I set the timeout to 15 seconds on the close the the hang went away , I have repeated the tests run 20 times without a hang now. &lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="108319" author="abilan" created="Wed, 1 Oct 2014 06:27:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do we need to do anything on the matter?&lt;br/&gt;
I think this race condition should be fixed in current Rabbit Client library&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
